        password. For example, if @c(peter-acc) is a bank account with password
        @c(open-sesame), then

        ..src > scheme
          (define paul-acc
            (make-joint peter-acc
                        'open-sesame
                        'rosebud))
        < src..

        will allow one to make transactions on @c(peter-acc) using the name
